name: | Continuation, World#0.5|
description:
| Continuation. | 
|"You think you've come a long way; you think everything happens for a reason from now on, that blinding flash of light hits you every time still, that shadow of yours would only make you wonder what's left behind and as you're chasing what's lost, you'd lose sight of all that’s ahead of you." – The journal said.
Still, you keep on going, you keep on surviving, you keep on continuing. |
|Happy half a year of HEN. |
